        <p class="style106" style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;"><font color="#ffffff" face="Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">the 
          moon and the stars,</font></p>
        <p class="style106" style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;"><font color="#ffffff" face="Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">which 
